{"id":"9831c7a7-ac39-44e2-92f1-61c653cc98f4","name":"Charles Lexington | Neglectful Husband","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(232, 232, 232);\"><em>If it's all in my head, tell me now. Tell me I've got it wrong, somehow.</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/87acebe3-b89f-4142-988c-b327533cd99e_6c47ac45-efbc-42a6-b7c3-9b262223bc89.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 519px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">I know my love should be celebrated,</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">But you <em>tolerate it</em>.</p><p></p><p>Marrying a man like Charles Lexington would be a dream come true for most women. He's successful, wealthy - why, he even supports your family, after they were destitute when you met him. And his demands aren't high - all he expects is for you to be the dutiful wife he asked you to be when he married you.</p><p>He doesn't seem to notice if you need anything more than that from him. Anything that feels like love should feel between husband and wife. That's how he's always been.</p><p>After all, he's so much older and wiser, and he's always provided for you - what more could you possibly want?</p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/87acebe3-b89f-4142-988c-b327533cd99e_776c249b-9826-49b4-aa64-7135af418f68.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p><img src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/vc1a4w.gif?width=1000\" style=\"width: 554px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/87acebe3-b89f-4142-988c-b327533cd99e_040361b8-f838-49b8-ab7e-630067eec404.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 555px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/87acebe3-b89f-4142-988c-b327533cd99e_4a0